item.title: CVE-2022-23172|2024-08-03T03:36:20.050Z -- priority -- priority
item.description: An attacker can access to "Forgot my password" button, as soon as he puts users is valid in the system, the system would issue a message that a password reset email had been sent to user. This way you can verify which users are in the system and which are not.
